{"id": "27891", "post": "<div class=\"post-27891 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-alma tag-alma-linux tag-racknerd tag-rocky tag-rocky-linux tag-solusvm\" id=\"post-27891\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/community-news-rocky-linux-os-now-available-on-racknerds-platform/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Community News: Rocky Linux OS Now Available on RackNerd\u2019s Platform!</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/alma/\" rel=\"tag\">alma</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/alma-linux/\" rel=\"tag\">alma linux</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/racknerd/\" rel=\"tag\">racknerd</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/rocky/\" rel=\"tag\">rocky</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/rocky-linux/\" rel=\"tag\">rocky linux</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/solusvm/\" rel=\"tag\">SolusVM</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> July 30, 2021 @ 12:00 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/racknerd_300.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-26267 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/racknerd_300.png.webp\" alt=\"RackNerd Logo\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/racknerd_300.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/racknerd_300-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/racknerd_300.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/racknerd_300-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"><a href=\"https://rockylinux.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"Rocky Linux\">Rocky Linux</a> offered their first official release (8.4) on June 21st and now providers are adding it as an option to their hosting platforms.&nbsp; If you\u2019re not familiar, Rocky Linux is CentOS Reborn.&nbsp; You can read up on <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/centos-rip-long-live-centos-stream/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"CentOS on LowEndBox\">our</a> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/centos-rhel-and-alma-the-plot-thickens/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"CentOS on LowEndBox\">previous</a> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lowendboxtv-centos-what-happened/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"CentOS on LowEndBox\">posts</a> about CentOS developments that necessitated remaking it.&nbsp; Rocky Linux is led by Gregory Kurtzer, founder of the CentOS project.</p><p>An alternative to Rocky Linux is <a href=\"https://almalinux.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"Alma Linux\">Alma Linux</a> (discussed in our <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/interview-with-igor-seletskiy-ceo-of-cloudlinux-on-project-lenix-centos-changes-and-much-more/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"LowEndBox Interview\">interview with Igor Seletskiy</a>).&nbsp; It remains to see which neo-CentOS wins in the long run or if they both remain viable.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.racknerd.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"RackNerd\">RackNerd</a> <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/172947/rocky-linux-now-available-on-our-kvm-vps-platform\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"RackNerd Announcement\">recently announced</a> that Rocky Linux is now officially available on their platform.&nbsp; They previously announced <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/community-news-almalinux-os-now-available-on-racknerds-platform/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"RackNerd Alma\">Alma Linux availability</a> as well.</p><p>Existing <a href=\"https://www.racknerd.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"RackNerd\">RackNerd</a> customers can reinstall their VPS to the new Rocky Linux OS template within minutes, using the SolusVM control panel. For those who prefer to install manually from an ISO, the Rocky Linux ISO can be mounted by request (just open a support ticket).</p><p><strong>What are your thoughts between Rocky Linux and AlmaLinux? Which do you prefer, and why? Share your thoughts below!</strong></p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/racknerd-los-angeles-kvm-vps-get-a-2-8-gb-ram-vps-with-58-gb-ssd-for-only-29-99-year/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"RackNerd Logo\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/racknerd_300-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">RackNerd - Los Angeles KVM VPS - Get a 2.8 GB RAM VPS with 58 GB SSD for Only $29.99/Year!</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lowendboxtv-weekend-update-for-july-17-2021/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"LEBTV Update\" style=\"background: transparent u